reviews.text: Traditional HK fast food style restaurant. Reasonable price, there are lots of thing to choose from in the menu. The 3 dishes rice set is their signature

食物十分好，地方乾淨

reviews.text: It’s a family run dessert shop. The desserts we ordered were great and sweetness was just right! Food variety was limited but definitely will come for 2nd time.
Cute little family-run dessert shop, their steamed coconuts are delicious and affordable! Worth every dollar on the bill!
In average its fine. Sizes for waffles is a bit small and thin. Durian Paste with steam egg white coconut water is good. Quite crowded after 10:30pm at night.
Excellent
